  <data name="labelQisDefense.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Qi's Defense is a real-time protection program that runs in the background on your computer.
Please note: this product is not antivirus software, nor should it be used as a substitute for one!

It mainly focuses on system repair and protection against rogue software and does not currently include virus-related protection measures.

Once you enable Qi's Defense, it will automatically start when your computer boots, run silently in the background, and consume very few resources.

*Some system issues will be checked each time you start your computer. A full check requires manual initiation.

*We also provide a feature to detect errors caused by other third-party software. However, Qizhi Defense itself does not have built-in repair capabilities — repairs are primarily performed by QisToolkit3</value>
